---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Tool Reviews" description="In-depth reviews of AI automation and cybersecurity tools.">
  <div class="container" style="padding: 4rem 0;">
    <h1 style="font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary) 0%, var(--primary-light) 100%); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text;">Tool Reviews</h1>
    <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 3rem;">
      Honest, data-driven reviews of the tools we've tested.
    </p>
    
    <div class="review-grid">
      <div class="review-card">
        <h3>HubSpot</h3>
        <p class="category">AI Automation • CRM</p>
        <p>All-in-one CRM and marketing automation platform. 30% recurring commission for 12 months.</p>
        <div class="tool-meta">
          <span>⭐ 4.5/5</span>
          <span>💰 High-ticket</span>
        </div>
        <a href="/blog/hubspot-vs-salesforce-2026" class="btn">Read Review →</a>
      </div>
      <div class="review-card">
        <h3>Scalenut</h3>
        <p class="category">AI Content • SEO</p>
        <p>SEO content lifecycle tool with AI-powered writing. 30-50% lifetime recurring commissions.</p>
        <div class="tool-meta">
          <span>⭐ 4.7/5</span>
          <span>💰 Lifetime</span>
        </div>
        <a href="/blog/best-ai-automation-tools-2026" class="btn">Read Review →</a>
      </div>
      <div class="review-card">
        <h3>NordLayer</h3>
        <p class="category">Cybersecurity • VPN</p>
        <p>Enterprise VPN with lifetime revenue share. Business-grade security for remote teams.</p>
        <div class="tool-meta">
          <span>⭐ 4.6/5</span>
          <span>🔒 Enterprise</span>
        </div>
        <a href="/blog/secure-automation-stack-guide" class="btn">Read Review →</a>
      </div>
      <div class="review-card">
        <h3>Surfshark</h3>
        <p class="category">Cybersecurity • VPN</p>
        <p>Consumer and SMB VPN with 60% commission. Affordable security for small teams.</p>
        <div class="tool-meta">
          <span>⭐ 4.6/5</span>
          <span>🔒 Business</span>
        </div>
        <a href="/blog/secure-automation-stack-guide" class="btn">Read Review →</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div style="margin-top: 4rem; padding: 2.5rem; background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 16px; text-align: center;">
      <h2 style="font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Can't find what you're looking for?</h2>
      <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Check our comprehensive guides and comparisons.</p>
      <a href="/blog" style="display: inline-block; padding: 1rem 2rem; background: var(--primary); color: #fff; border-radius: 10px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;">Browse All Articles →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .review-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .review-card {
    padding: 2rem;
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    transition: all 0.3s;
    backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
  }

  .review-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--primary);
    transform: translateY(-5px);
  }

  .review-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .category {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .review-card p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .tool-meta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .btn {
    display: inline-block;
    color: var(--primary);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .btn:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>
